<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I don&apos;t know of any such book though, in the aforementioned book there is an assay named &quot;Thus Spoke the Crow&quot;and that&apos;s hugely inspirational.<br/><a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I don't know of any such book though, in the aforementioned book there is an assay named "Thus Spoke the Crow"and that's hugely inspirational.<br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
