<span id="freeTextContainer5738972329372753343">This book,as the name suggests, compiles some of the best works of Ruskin. The beauty of Bond’s writings lie in the simplicity of thoughts and clear presentation to the readers . He mostly writes on his own days, childhood, adulthood and on his contemporary times. He has beautifully put moments in stories which sometimes seems to be a mundane routine in one’s life. It is clear that a writer certainly has keen observatory skills over an average human being. Sometimes repetitions are visible but t</span>
  <span id="freeText5738972329372753343" style="display:none">This book,as the name suggests, compiles some of the best works of Ruskin. The beauty of Bond’s writings lie in the simplicity of thoughts and clear presentation to the readers . He mostly writes on his own days, childhood, adulthood and on his contemporary times. He has beautifully put moments in stories which sometimes seems to be a mundane routine in one’s life. It is clear that a writer certainly has keen observatory skills over an average human being. Sometimes repetitions are visible but these can be neglected. </span>
