<span id="freeTextContainer18386894225734177944">An excellent compendium of Ruskin Bond&apos;s charming stories deeply infused with the spirit of North India. I got this book inscribed by the author himself at Mussoorie, and was struck by his simplicity and warmth. For a flavour of the the Himalayas, and of growing up in India, you can&apos;t do better than Ruskin Bond. And no better way to read his work, than curled up by a fireside on a winter evening in Mussoorie after a hike down to the bazaar.</span>
  <span id="freeText18386894225734177944" style="display:none">An excellent compendium of Ruskin Bond's charming stories deeply infused with the spirit of North India. I got this book inscribed by the author himself at Mussoorie, and was struck by his simplicity and warmth. For a flavour of the the Himalayas, and of growing up in India, you can't do better than Ruskin Bond. And no better way to read his work, than curled up by a fireside on a winter evening in Mussoorie after a hike down to the bazaar.</span>
