<span id="freeTextContainer930979611856844530">I don&apos;t know why it took me so long to revisit Ruskin bond&apos;s stories. I saw this title while looking for a random read. And It came back, all at once, the way I felt when I read Night train at deoli. I read it when I was in school and beauty of it still haunts me. stories will captivate you and narration fires your imagination and yet beauty of his stories is, they will stay with you forever after as if you have lived a lifetime through a character.</span>
